<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多特服装店里，潘瑟和简不理对方了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一条非常漂亮的裙子。”店主多特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你。这正是我想要的。”潘瑟说，但她却瞪着简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得你穿它看上去很胖。”简用刻薄的声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们女生应该对彼此好一点。你们不是姐妹吗？”多特问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但潘瑟和简都不回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时在游戏店里，赛伊已经准备好为他买的游戏付钱了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58373</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的购物总金额是一千零五十六美元外加七十一美分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>店员懒洋洋地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70850</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊停了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，那换成金币是多少？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说什么？你是说金币吗？”店员问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。我的包里只有金币。”赛伊指着他的包说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一半是我的。”鲍比生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起！”店员说，“但我们只接受现金、信用卡或支票。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这些金币值很多钱啊。”赛伊拿着一枚金币恳求说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那看上去像游戏币。”店员说着从赛伊手里拿过了金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们是真的金币，我跟你说。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊争辩说，但店员并不相信他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简有点想哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这不公平。”她默默地想着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么潘瑟想做什么都要去做？我也有钱啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这件裙子的价格是二十一美元六十美分。”多特微笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好！”潘瑟回答。她开始数出一些金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的，我们这里不收外币哦！”多特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些不是外币。”潘瑟笑了，“这些是金币啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多特有些怀疑，拿起一块金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们从哪里弄到这些的？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟回答之前看了简一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我叔叔给的。他给了我们这些金币作为礼物。”潘瑟撒谎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>多特眯起了眼睛盯着潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“待在这里别动。我要去打个电话。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，多特就去了店后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟抓住简的手臂迅速地小声说：“简！我觉得她去报警了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简双臂交叉回答说：“我不在意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你才是有麻烦的那个，又不是我。我没买裙子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237049</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>游戏商店里的情况也没好多少。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拜托啦！先生！”赛伊继续和店员争辩着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看，我会把这里所有的金币都给你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们的价值都超过五千美元了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不公平！”鲍比叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里面有些是我的钱！我要买车的！”鲍比抓住了包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放开，你个小笨蛋！”赛伊大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男孩儿们开始把包抢来抢去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>结果那个背包就像裂开的西瓜一样裂成了两半，金币洒了一地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在多特服装店里，潘瑟不得不迅速做出决定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简，我们必须离开这里。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟抓起她的手臂把她从店里拽了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回来，女孩们！”多特大叫着朝他们跑来。“我说了，回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简都没回头看一眼，用她们最快的速度跑走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>游戏商店的店员现在非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要叫警察了！”他威胁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”赛伊颤抖着声音问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为你们用假钱。”店员回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但这是真的。这是真的金子啊，我告诉你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊争辩说，但一切都是无用功。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>